  "instructions": [
    "Heat olive oil in a large saucepan over medium heat.",
    "Add onions and garlic, sautéing until translucent.",
    "Stir in smoked paprika and cumin; cook for about 1 minute.",
    "Add split peas and water or broth. Bring to a boil, then reduce heat to low, cover, and simmer for 20 minutes.",
